sections.heading: Board, defined.Prior to July 1, 2026, board means the Board of Advanced Practice Registered Nurses
sections.text: Beginning July 1, 2026, board means the Board of Nursing.SourceLaws 1981, LB 379, § 5;Laws 1996, LB 414, § 15;Laws 2000, LB 1115, § 30;R.S.1943, (2003), § 71-1708;Laws 2007, LB463, § 798;Laws 2025, LB
